---
By: Nathaniel Hawthorne
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 152
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Faith
---
Faith is a grand cathedral, with divinely pictured windows. Standing
without, you see no glory, nor can imagine any, but standing within, every
ray of light reveals a harmony of unspeakable splendors.
